HERE YOU MUST SUPPLY A ROUTINE TO CALCULATE THE LOCAL DELTA FUNCTION
THAT HAS TO BE FITTED AGAINST THE IMPURITY DELTA FUNCTION
in general \DELTA_LOCAL = G_0LOCAL - i\OME - \MU

SOME EXAMPLES OF WORKING ROUTINES ARE PROVIDED IN THIS DIRECTORY

\DELTA_LOCAL FUNCTION MUST BE STORED IN THE ARRAY delta(:) 
TO BE ALLOCATED IN THE ROUTINE.
